data.description: When house hunting, are you imagining a serene cul-de-sac where community bonds are tight and traffic is scarce? Introducing 13046 Cedar Creek Trail, a delightful 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence nestled in the sought-after Talise-De-Culebra neighborhood. Embraced by lush, mature trees, the inviting front porch sets the scene for tranquil mornings, perfect for savoring your morning coffee while enjoying the birdsong. Step inside to discover an inviting and spacious floor plan. To your right, a formal dining area awaits, perfect for hosting memorable gatherings and dinners with loved ones. Straight ahead lies the heart of the home - a cozy living space seamlessly connected to the kitchen. The kitchen itself is a culinary haven, featuring ample cabinet space, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, gas cooking, and a walk-in pantry. Noteworthy is the oversized kitchen island with a dual-sided breakfast bar, offering both functionality and additional seating. A unique highlight is the built-in desk/convenient kitchen office center, ideal for various tasks such as homework, work projects, or organizing daily schedules. Say goodbye to laundry woes with the utility sink in the laundry room, offering hassle-free hand washing or pre-soaking for delicate items. Plus, it's perfect for filling Fido's water bowl or tending to indoor greenery! The primary suite impresses with its spaciousness and spa-like ensuite bathroom, complete with an oversized walk-in shower complete with separate shower heads, dual sink vanity, and walk-in closet. But the piece de resistance? A balcony off the primary suite, offering a retreat where you can relax and unwind. Upstairs, you'll find two well-appointed secondary bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a spacious loft, providing additional living space for relaxation or recreation. The backyard is an entertainer's paradise, featuring abundant space, mature trees, and no rear neighbors, promising endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment and gatherings. Residents of this neighborhood enjoy access to top-notch amenities, including a pool, clubhouse, basketball court, and playground, enhancing the quality of life in this desirable community. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
